---
const faqs = [
  {
    q: 'Has anyone actually built and run this?',
    a: 'Yes. The core platform — wizard, dashboard, scheduling, installer view, and customer follow-up flows — is installed and running at Fitchin Automotive Detailing & Window Tinting in Coshocton, Ohio. You can visit their site and submit a real quote through the wizard right now. Your build will be a custom configuration of the same core platform.',
  },
  {
    q: 'Is this just a website?',
    a: 'No. The website or landing page is part of the system, but the main value is the quote or booking flow itself.',
  },
  {
    q: 'Where do the leads go?',
    a: "Into a dashboard built for shop owners. Every quote, partial lead, and booking lands there in real time. Open it on your phone between jobs, assign work to your tech, mark jobs complete, and see what's converting.",
  },
  {
    q: 'Do my customers get an automatic reply?',
    a: 'Yes. The moment a quote is submitted, the customer gets an auto-text and an auto-email confirming you received it. Bookings get a confirmation plus a reminder before the appointment. After a job is marked complete, the customer gets a review request. SMS features are configured with proper customer consent language and carrier requirements as part of your build.',
  },
  {
    q: 'Can my installer or tech see only their jobs?',
    a: "Yes. There's a separate installer login that shows only the jobs assigned to that person, on their phone. They can mark jobs complete from the truck. Owner sees everything; installer sees only what's assigned.",
  },
  {
    q: 'Can I change my own prices?',
    a: 'Yes. Pricing lives in your dashboard. Change a price, the wizard updates instantly. Add a service, a package, or an add-on without a dev call.',
  },
  {
    q: 'Can I use my own logo and brand colors?',
    a: 'Yes. Upload your logo, pick your brand color, the wizard and landing page update everywhere — including customer emails.',
  },
  {
    q: 'Do I own my data?',
    a: "Yes. Your leads, quotes, bookings, and customer data belong to you. If you ever leave, we'll provide a full export of your data on the way out.",
  },
  {
    q: 'Do I need a brand-new website?',
    a: "Usually not. The wizard can be embedded into an existing site, or delivered with a focused landing page wrapper. If your full site needs rebuilt, that's scoped separately.",
  },
  {
    q: 'What happens to my founding rate after the 3 spots fill?',
    a: 'Founding clients keep their locked-in monthly rate for as long as they stay subscribed and the scope stays the same. When standard pricing goes up, your monthly rate stays the same.',
  },
  {
    q: "I'm already on Square (or another booking system). Can the wizard work with that?",
    a: "Sometimes — depends on your setup. The standard Wizard build replaces your contact form and booking flow entirely. If you're already on Square and want to keep payments and core booking there, we can sometimes layer the wizard's lead capture and follow-up onto your existing setup instead of replacing it. Scope and pricing differ from the standard Wizard — reach out and we'll talk.",
  },
  {
    q: 'Who is this for?',
    a: 'Local service businesses with real pricing logic — packages, add-ons, or job-size variables. Not for brand-new startups, e-commerce, or businesses without a clear service catalog.',
  },
  {
    q: 'I own a window tint shop. Should I be here or at TintShopLaunch?',
    a: "TintShopLaunch. It's the same wizard pattern, productized for tint pricing, with lower setup. Designed to Elevate is for everything else.",
    tintLink: true,
  },
  {
    q: 'Do you run Google Ads or do SEO?',
    a: 'The Wizard build includes the landing page and tracking — both designed to be ad-ready. Ad management itself is a separate engagement once we know the page is converting. Same for ongoing SEO.',
  },
  {
    q: 'Why is there a monthly fee?',
    a: 'It covers hosting, technical upkeep, small improvements, tracking checks, and pricing-rule edits. It keeps the system supported after launch.',
  },
  {
    q: "What if I'm not ready for the full Wizard?",
    a: "Start with the 14-Day Sprint. Most clients use it to see what's broken and decide whether the Wizard is the right next step.",
  },
];
---
<!-- FAQ SECTION -->
<section id="faq" class="relative border-b border-line">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-5 sm:px-8 py-20 sm:py-28">
    <div>
      <span class="eyebrow"><span class="dot" aria-hidden="true"></span> FAQ</span>
      <h2 class="mt-5 text-[2rem] sm:text-[2.6rem] leading-[1.05] font-bold">
        Common Questions
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-5 text-text-soft text-[1.05rem] leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
        If something's not answered here, call or text Bill at
        <a href="tel:7406176488" class="text-accent font-medium underline decoration-accent/40 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-accent transition-colors whitespace-nowrap">(740) 617-6488</a>.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 space-y-3">
      {faqs.map((f) => (
        <details class="faq-item card group p-0 overflow-hidden">
          <summary class="cursor-pointer list-none flex items-start justify-between gap-4 px-6 py-5 sm:px-7 sm:py-6 select-none">
            <span class="font-display font-semibold text-[1.02rem] sm:text-[1.08rem] text-text leading-snug">{f.q}</span>
            <span class="mt-0.5 inline-flex h-7 w-7 items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-line text-text-soft group-hover:border-accent group-hover:text-accent transition-colors flex-shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg class="faq-chevron transition-transform duration-200" width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
            </span>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-6 sm:px-7 sm:pb-7 -mt-1">
            <p class="text-[0.95rem] text-text-soft leading-relaxed max-w-prose">
              {f.a}
              {f.tintLink && (
                <>
                  {' '}
                  <a href="https://tintshoplaunch.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent font-medium underline decoration-accent/40 underline-offset-4 hover:decoration-accent transition-colors">Visit TintShopLaunch ↗</a>
                </>
              )}
            </p>
          </div>
        </details>
      ))}
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
      <a href="#apply" class="btn-primary">
        Apply for a Wizard Build
        <span aria-hidden="true">↗</span>
      </a>
      <a href="tel:7406176488" class="btn-ghost">
        <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72c.13.96.36 1.9.7 2.81a2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45c.91.34 1.85.57 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92Z"/></svg>
        Call or Text Bill
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .faq-item summary::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }
  .faq-item[open] .faq-chevron { transform: rotate(180deg); }
  .faq-item[open] { border-color: rgba(255, 107, 26, 0.4); }
</style>
<!-- /FAQ SECTION -->
